These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Pet       | guinea-pig       | hamster |
| Color         | fuchsia | pink  |
| Beverage       | milk    | 7up    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, cabbage
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, ritmeester
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, train
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | cabbage     | kiwi |
| Cigar           | chaman | ritmeester      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Transport         | skateboard | train     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra
City: new-york, edinburgh
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Sport          | volleyball    | basketball   |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | oliveros   |
| City     | edinburgh     | new-york |

