3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Color          | azure         | lavender    |
| Flower           | sunflower | bellflower    |
| City   | san-francisco           | boston   |

