.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Flower           | tulip | rose     |
| Music-Genre   | pop          | r&b |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Birthday     | october            | may       |

 